sub_title: Humanitarian | Pediatrician | Founder & CEO of CREDOCOR & CoMaster | Co-Founder Hozan Zangana Studio
summary:
Founder & CEO of CoMaster, which aims to innovate and digitalize medical education & communication by creating inclusive and accessible content on our YouTube channel.

Co-Founder and CFO of Hozan Zangana Studio specialized in heritage based contemporary art & design.

Consultant in Pediatrics with special focus on Gastro-Enterology, Functional Somatic Disorders (FSD) and Obesity. Certified in the field of Integrative medicine with special focus on medical hypnosis and mind-body connection.

Chair of the Board of EKANN, which aims to improve the health of refugee children in the Netherlands.

Certified educationalist in the field of Medical Education, Inclusive Communication and Diversity, Inclusivity & Equity. Instructor in Neonatal Life Support (NLS). Certified as a Medical Coach, Peer Supporter and Mentor of (junior) doctors.
